chapters/slick.html.title: slick
chapters/slick.html.body:
slick
使用示例

更新 slick

if (!whole.localeSlick) {
  whole.localeSlick = $('#localeSlick').slick({
    autoplay: false,
    autoplaySpeed: 3000,
    // arrows: false,
    // appendArrows: '',
    // prevArrow: '',
    // nextArrow: '',
    infinite: false,
  });
} else {
  whole.localeSlick.slick('setPosition');
}


设置自定义箭头按钮

$('.slider').slick({
  appendArrows: $('.slider-container'),
  prevArrow: 'prev',
  nextArrow: 'next',
  infinite: false,
  slidesToShow: 8,
  slidesToScroll: 8,
});
